                    ddn: 'na |ma | a |nna|a n| ka|ka | ba|a a|a b| n | ma| nn|ama|om |yom|ni | bЙ”|a k| da|i k| go|daa|a d| ku|aam|gon|a m|i n|nЙӣ |a s| hi|Йӣi |iya|rЙ” |Й”rЙ”|mЙӣi|ara| sa|bЙ”r|a g|aa |a h| ga|inЙӣ| za|fЙ” |ayo|onn|ya |ra | bi|ani|iyo|Й”ЕӢЙ”|bЙ”ЕӢ|bam|kul| fЙ”|nЙ” |yo |amЙӣ| di|ri |ini|ei | nЙ”|a t|lu |ulu|waa| kw|ii | si|ari|una|ЕӢЙ” |hin|bin| na|si |sЙӣ |a c|riy|Й” n|kun|ba | sЙӣ|wei|aar|i b|i g|ga |Йӣ a| ta|kwa|Йӣ b|i s|a f| ci|Й” b|n m|tЙӣ |Й”u | ya| du|sar|u b|m d|u g|Й” k|sii|iri|u n|ЙӣrЙӣ|i d|gwe|a z|u k| su|ЕӢa | tЙӣ|m n|bu | de|niy| gw|bar|asi|taa|di |ono|su |Й” s| mЙӣ| cЙӣ|rЙӣ |ali|no |n s|Й” f|uyo|Йӣ n|ima|i h|baa|abu|hЙӣi| hЙӣ|o z|zam| ЕӢw| ti|i t|aab|ko |li |aal|man|Й” g|Йӣiy|las|n b|oo |nni|ila|til| Й”u| ko|a y|o d|o b|Йӣ g|gan|ci |sЙ”u|isЙ”|fis| fi| be|aЕӢa|Й” m|him|yan|cЙӣr| mЙ”|cou| co|eri|eer|maa|o k|saa| ji| se|Йӣ d|i m|u a|ee |dee|wЙ” | wЙ”|mi |imi|zaЕӢ|am |asa| la|Й” d|a w|uur|zaa|yaa|ana|u s|nan|ЕӢu |ann|ЙӣtЙӣ|e b|m b|dim|ЙӣЙӣ |eiy|bei|aka|n g|ЙӣnЙӣ|ЕӢwЙӣ|oyo|o g|uri|duu|u h|a ЕӢ| al|enn|sen|Йӣ h|a j|du |i c|kaa|uma|rum|Йӣru|ala|yay| bЙӣ|Й”Й”r|nay|dii| ha|i a|i f|Й”Й” |Йӣ k|i y|laa|Йӣ f|tЙӣr|cin|dam|gu | ad|la |ouy|Йӣ m|aas|wЙӣn|inn|ada| ni|aay|loo| lo|ant|ina| fe|ti |aat|je |ije|iij|hii|ta |ЕӢwa|o n|n k| nu|i z|m k|isi|jis|wЙӣ |i Й”|osi|oos|goo|u c',
