                    wwa: ' o | da| yi|da |ma |a o|iri|yir|ri |ba |na |a y|i d| ba| ta| nМҖ|o n|i y|ro |ki |nМҖ |i o|a d|a s|di | i |sar|ris|bГ  | bГ |o t|aro|isa|a m|a t| di| ma|ta | na|a n| ka| sa| bo|an |o b|ka | ya|a b|ook| nЙӣ| ti|sa |a i|i t|oki|wan| wa| tЙ”|i b|a k|soo| so|aa |o w|ii |de |ti |ori|maa|nЙӣk|mii|ima| to|ari|Йӣki| mi|re | de| ye|o y|МҖ y|i s| yo| fЙ”|o d|tor|ku |mma|tin|si |i m|i n|rim|ya |i k|nde|paa|yon|tЙ”Й”|imm|e d|kpa|n o|o k|ama|aam|yaa|oti|tir|yi |iro|aar|daa|Й”ba|Й”Й”b|den|n d|aan|nkp|ink|yer|ЙӣЙӣn|isi|a p|oma|fЙ”Й”|bo | mЙӣ|uri|Й”Й”r| nЙ”|su |rik|on |yee|ire| te|eri|u y|sim|oot|boo|aba|aЕӢi|o o|Й”ku|Й”Й”k|o i|Йӣ o|Г  t|mЙӣЙӣ|Й”ri|n t|nЙ”Й”|en |onn|tan|eet|e n| ku|e m|pЙӣЙӣ| pЙӣ|o p|n b|Йӣnd|МҖ b|asi|ЕӢis|yaЕӢ|u d|tu |ra |nda|sir| co|ina|fЙ” |yin|ЙӣЙӣ |n n|kЙ”Й”| kЙ”| sЙ”|sab| su|bar|eti|Г  d|and|wo | wo|yoЕӢ|tЙ” |ЕӢa |e y|Й”Й”t|Йӣ b|u t|a w|Йӣ y|ara|ЙӣМғЙӣ|wЙӣМғ| wЙӣ|e s|bot|bom|ond|nsi|u n|o f|Й” d|are| si|iba|rib|iya|riy|dur|ГЈdu| ГЈd|too|kpЙӣ|o s|Й”ya|i c|tim|Й”ti|sЙ”Й”|ika|tak|u s|kir|uki|puk| pu|oon|coo|ato|aat|kaa|Й”Й”s|yГ¬ | yГ¬|n y|tet|Г  y| pe| do|ne |nne|МҖ t|e t|ЕӢo |oЕӢo|dЙӣЙӣ|te |ete|uti|kut| kp| mu|Йӣmb|ЙӣЙӣm|yЙӣЙӣ| yЙӣ|tee|Г  k|kar|ni |nni|Г  o|nna|ann|dan| pa|a c|Йӣ d|a f|nЙӣ |i f|nri|inr|ena|een| se|Г  m|Й”Й” |okp|sЙӣs|a ГЈ|Й” f|Йӣti|in |emm|dem| tu|Йӣ n|sЙӣ ',
